ldnt be nearly as much and you could look into putting the money elsewhere, some nice PoP items no doubt (like that new very nice droppable earring). Other nice quests worth researching doable by a small guild include the Strength of the Elements quest (15ac 15str FR/CR 100hp shoulders) and 9th coldain ring (forget stats but a significant upgrade over 6/65).<br>
